                        grosz, und also hat der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> armmanne yeder die
                                <expan>vorges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> sein hab vor uns czu den
                                <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt, daz die sein sey.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hilff und <expan>fürdu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darczu
